      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Isolated mitochondria were resuspended in solubilization buffer (50 mM NaCl, 50 mM imidazole, 2 mM 6-aminohexanonic acid, and 1 mM EDTA) and lysed for 15 min at 4°C by addition of 1% dodecyl-maltoside or 2.6% digitonin, respectively [CITATION_1] ."
